name: testAppointmentCancellationWorkflowWithValidationErrors
description:
Use internal API to test the following workflow:
- save appointment
- list of appointments
- introduce appointment request
- compose appointment request message
- review invalid appointment request message
- review valid appointment request message
- send invalid appointment request message
- send valid appointment request message
- confirm appointment request
- finish appointment request
